"avatar"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"user addressbook management"
,
"cn"
:
"用户地址薄管理"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x tea avatar add <key> <user_path>"
,
"en"
:
"Add the user <user_path> to the addressbook of the current session"
,
"cn"
:
"添加 user <user_path> 到当前会话的 addressbook"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x tea repo collaborator add --repo <owner_repo> <key>"
,
"en"
:
"Using <key> recorded in the address book <user_path> to add the user as a repository collaborator"
,
"cn"
:
"使用用户地址薄 <key> 记录的 <user_path> 来添加为仓库成员"
}
]
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://fjo/data/common/avatar.jso"
}
,
"--cur"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"current session default value management"
,
"cn"
:
"当前会话默认值管理"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://fjo/data/common/cur.jso"
}
,
"--cfg"
:
{
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://tea/data/common/cfg.jso"
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"manage configuration for tea"
,
"cn"
:
"tea 配置管理"
}
,
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Get gitea access token: https://gitea.com/user/settings/applications\ndefault endpoint: https://gitea.com/api/v1\ndefault web_endpoint: https://gitea.com/\n"
,
"cn"
:
"gitea 私人令牌获取: https://gitea.com/user/settings/applications\n默认 endpoint (API 访问端点): https://gitea.com/api/v1\n默认 web_endpoint (网站访问端点): https://gitea.com/\n"
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"When you need to switch between the config and profile, Need to use current to switch\n\n`x tea --cur <config|profile>=<switch_val>`\n"
,
"cn"
:
"当你需要切换使用的 config 和 profile 时候, 需要使用 `current` 进行切换\n\n`x tea --cur <config|profile>=<switch_val>`\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x tea --cfg token=<token>"
,
"en"
:
"Setup gitea access token for default initialization"
,
"cn"
:
"添加私人令牌, 进行默认初始化"
}
]
}
,
"init"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Initialize the configuration using interactive mode"
,
"cn"
:
"使用交互模式初始化配置"
}
}
,
